description: This Chainlink VRF common Gaston purrs with a rating of 57, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 57, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Stringalong for North, 5 for East, Leverage for South, and Box for West. Gaston has the personality suit of whale. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/60571-75640-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gaston [57 Votes, Common]
